{"tid":1722129,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（純學術討論，不鬧戰）Poly嚴控唔畀咁多外人入黎，做法係咪好過暴大？","createTime":"2019-11-14T22:59:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-14T23:33:51.000Z","uid":171506,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"5dac96a4c31a75aeddd45a48dd6875e3f7bfc3f3","tid":1722129,"uid":171506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T22:59:12.000Z","msg":"開放一條行車線，未必係錯，但如果三條友身份不明，會唔會係試水溫？<br />\n<br />\n如果下次有另外三個蒙面人係凌晨三點宣布，校園抗爭正式結束，以配合區議會選舉，咁點處理？<br />\n<br />\nPoly果種做法，有疑問就唔畀外人進入，係咪值得其他大學借鏡？<br />\n<br />\n是否只限學生，舊生，同其他大學學生進入指定範圍，要show證為準？<br />\n<br />\n一般市民是否只能送物資？邊一個地點接收，放低就走的話，係咪唔駛搜身？<br />\n<br />\n要預先諗定，其他大學稍後可能都會有同樣問題。<br />\n<br />\n經過接近半年，政府對於無大台的運作方式，應該已有透徹理解，開始知道點應對，大家要小心行事。"},{"pid":"4e7800e308af20b9bc0dc2417ca60e6c689e7d03","tid":1722129,"uid":125502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T23:00:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0BmJSfv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0BmJSfv.png&h=cb5bad6d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>旭日三罷行動</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />記住食飽啲先有體力<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />作戰係長期嘅記住有咩事注意安全先<br />\n<br />\n詳細資訊同集合資訊可參考：<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/dnlmcarrielam\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fdnlmcarrielam&d=KYS9j8ljDCWJrVyje8%2BOjeUDsY8FkShsNjUL6uXjEIs%3D&h=451ea2c9\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/dnlmcarrielam</a>"},{"pid":"518620983086d8e8246dee41d98b2da976e96889","tid":1722129,"uid":171506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T23:33:51.000Z","msg":"推"}]}